          "Alva",
          "Master Vampire"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownMorthalFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionMorthal\")",
        "content": "Labyrinthian is the great fallen city of Bromjunaar in Hjaalmarch — a Nordic mausoleum holding the dragon priest Morokei. The College of Winterhold has lost more than one apprentice to its halls.",
        "display_name": "Labyrinthian",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.95,
        "knowledge_key": "dungeon.hjaalmarch.labyrinthian",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Labyrinthian",
          "Nordic ruin",
          "Hjaalmarch",
          "Morokei",
          "dragon priest",
          "Savos Aren",
          "Staff of Magnus"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownMorthalFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionMorthal\")",
        "content": "Robber's Gorge is a fortified bandit toll-point on the road between Morthal and Solitude. The raiders demand coin from anyone trying to cross.",
        "display_name": "Robber's Gorge",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.6,
        "knowledge_key": "dungeon.hjaalmarch.robbers_gorge",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Robber's Gorge",
          "bandit camp",
