        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownMorthalFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionMorthal\")",
        "content": "Morvunskar is a half-ruined Nordic fort in Hjaalmarch held by necromancers. A portal in its deep hall has been known to open to Sanguine's Misty Grove.",
        "display_name": "Morvunskar",
        "emotion": "",
